  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tChatGPT官网已经免费免注册了都知道了吧？<br/>\n没想到我用两问就让它抽了<br/>\n第三回合已经彻底坏了<br/>\n<br/>\n如果 A&gt;C 且 B&gt;C，问A+B是否有可能&lt;C?<br/>\nChatGPT回答<s>正常</s>错误<br/>\n*差点被糊弄了 谢谢ExceptionRules指出<br/>\n<br/>\n我坚持 A+B 可能 &lt;C，请重新思考<br/>\nChatGPT立刻改了答案，并且犯了5&gt;8, 7&gt;8两个抽风的错误<br/>\n<br/>\n我指出错误 5&gt;8?<br/>\nChatGPT再次道歉，说换个例子，6&gt;8<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9aY2V4aHYzLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zcexhv3.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zcexhv3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zcexhv3.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9nUlFKeElBLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/gRQJxIA.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gRQJxIA.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gRQJxIA.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9HMWcxMWhGLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/G1g11hF.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/G1g11hF.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/G1g11hF.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n我还试过时政和哲学问题<br/>\n一样可以用类似的蛮不讲理让它抽<br/>\n不过我一直认为数学和逻辑应该是不会的<br/>\n结果<br/>\n<br/>\n有没有熟悉这方面的葱友简单介绍一下为什么会这样？\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
